00:01:18,498 --> 00:01:23,335
but we should also mention
geothermal energy

19
00:01:23,574 --> 00:01:28,337
that is increasingly important 
in cities, as well as, 

20
00:01:28,533 --> 00:01:31,033
energy produced from waste. 

21
00:01:31,876 --> 00:01:35,913
Then, we have much more 
efficient, 

22
00:01:36,128 --> 00:01:39,128
energy efficient 
consumption patterns, 

