68
00:04:43,902 --> 00:04:47,015
those are the actors that 
feed the electricity 

69
00:04:47,245 --> 00:04:51,633
into the city and at times may even 
take back electricity 

70
00:04:51,824 --> 00:04:55,762
to be stored in one of the dams 
